data.description: MLS# 273046 It's here! Country Living & less than 10 minutes from town! 623 Moore Rd, Pasco, WA – a 3-bed (master bedroom present), 2 full bath (Don't miss the Large soak-in tub in master!), 1,344 sqft double-wide manufactured home built in 2003. Situated on 5 acres. This property is ideal for those seeking to reap the rewards of both modern & rural living. Bring your cows, horses, chickens.. you name it! New year .. new home? Schedule a showing before it sells! See you soon
